  <brief_title>Mobilaser Study to Help With People Who Are Having Problems With Their Gait</brief_title>
  <official_title>Increasing Mobility in Parkinsonian Patients With Freezing of Gait and Gait Hypokinesia With an Adjustable, Attachable Laser (Mobilaser)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
