  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Does use of the Mobilaser reduce freezing of gait (FOG) and stride reduction in patients with
      Parkinson's disease and Parkinsonism.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Can patients walk faster and have less freezing when using the mobilaser then when not using
      it
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
